The paper proposes a neural network model with an external memory mechanism that leverages metalearning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions applications in natural language processing (NLP) and reinforcement learning (RL), which could place it in sub-categories such as cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
